    "body": "Sure, just import `hardhat` explicitly in your tests. \r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst {ethers} = require(\"hardhat\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nThere's [this guide](https://hardhat.org/guides/vscode-tests.html) for running them in vscode, it should also work for intellij. ",
